WARNING: Some of the testimony referred to in this judgment is graphic. Discretion is advised. This livestream has ended. You can watch the recording above. PRETORIA - The Gauteng North High Court delivered judgment in the Dros rape trial. Nicholas Ninow has pleaded guilty to two counts of rape and possession of drugs. He is accused of raping an eight-year-old girl at the Dros restaurant bathroom in Silverton, Pretoria.